    /// <summary>
    /// Presentation amount after sign convention applied:
    /// Assets/Expenses = debit-positive kept as-is.
    /// Liabilities/Equity/Income = flipped to show positive when credit balance.
    /// X3, X4 = shown negative (deductions).
